reviewText: It took longer than usual for standard delivery.  Came with extraordinary package. The screen out lay was alright and show was good...But the most disappointing thing ..It is toooooo short.  Could you imagine, the length only 15 minutes, I wrote this review because i do not want you to be disappointed in terms of the length...Love Grenada!.... :))
The DVD was defective, but from what I could view of it, it was not worth it.  Don't waste your money ...
